OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud and fog in the
OL,6,Fsoutheast clears to bring warm sunny
OL,7,Fspells. A band of rain moves
OL,8,Feastwards. Turning much cooler behind
OL,9,Fwith blustery showers, some heavy with
OL,10,Fhail, thunder, and snow over northern
OL,11,Fhigh ground.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers persist across
OL,14,Fnorthern and northwestern Scotland
OL,15,Fovernight. Elsewhere largely dry with
OL,16,Flong clear spells, cloud increasing
OL,17,Flater in the south and west. A colder
OL,18,Fnight brings patchy rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
