OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FWintry showers affect northern
OL,6,FScotland early. Elsewhere, a cold
OL,7,Fstart in the sunshine. Later, heavy
OL,8,Frain and strong winds spread from
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland into the west, with
OL,10,Fcoastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
